{
    "story_id": "",
    "story_icon": "",
    "outline": {
        "title": "",
        "content": [
            "要跳过此剧情吗？"
        ]
    },
    "story_content": [
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "add_book_text",
            "context": "幻影的另一面　后篇",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "add_book_text",
            "context": "“幽影”——\\n那是曾被人类\\n封印在异界空间的龙。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": "BOOK_210045_01"
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "add_book_text",
            "context": "不……现在已不再是龙。\\n自被当作灾厄的元凶讨伐\\n而化作幻影以来，\\n已经经历了多少岁月呢。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "add_book_text",
            "context": "幻影不抱有任何希望，\\n也没有任何梦想。\\n尽管如此，幽影的心里\\n也依旧留有一丝微弱的火焰。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "add_book_text",
            "context": "想品尝被人爱着的滋味。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "add_book_text",
            "context": "啊，多么贪婪的欲望啊。\\n区区幻影竟还敢渴望被爱。\\n根本没有人会注意到自己。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "add_book_text",
            "context": "正当他这么劝慰自己时，\\n白衣女孩轻盈地在黑暗中起舞。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "add_book_text",
            "context": "轻轻地，轻轻地，\\n舞姬跳着舞。\\n宛如划破黑暗的月光，\\n美丽而耀眼。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "add_book_text",
            "context": "“你是……”\\n她注意到了\\n本不会被发现的幻影。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "add_book_text",
            "context": "“你的模样好怪啊。”\\n被舞姬看到样貌的他以为……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "add_book_text",
            "context": "一切都完了。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "add_book_text",
            "context": "但舞姬并未离去。\\n那一缕光芒，\\n缓缓地落在了黑暗的身躯上。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "add_book_text",
            "context": "“你……不怕我吗？”\\n“为什么要怕你呢？\\n我都没跟你说过话。”",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "add_book_text",
            "context": "舞姬并没有\\n因对方外表丑陋就妄下定论。\\n她所观察的是内在与灵魂。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "add_book_text",
            "context": "注视自己的眼瞳与感受到的温暖\\n让早已化为幻影的他，重新回到了现实。\\n或许……如果是她……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "add_book_text",
            "context": "即便是幻影，\\n也忍不住想拥有梦想。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "add_book_text",
            "context": "“幽影”——",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "add_book_text",
            "context": "从那一刻起，幻影变回了龙。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        }
    ]
}